==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Atoll
<hw>A*toll"</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[The native name in
the Indian Ocean.]</ety> <def>A coral island or islands, consisting of a
belt of coral reef, partly submerged, surrounding a central lagoon or
depression; a lagoon island.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

